	(text "This is fine but it means you are resetting them both at the same time. \nIf you are planning to reset these often, then a large visible switch for each one is nice.\nIf you are only planning to reset them once or twice, then just use a jumper cable and connecting it GND when you need to."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 111.506 176.784 0)
